{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354000/extras/Slackers_B2_First_Downhill.jpg?t=1734729744\" /><br><br><i>When the drinks stop flowing and the city store's closing its doors, who are you gonna call to save the day? Come roll with our crew of laid-back slackers, ready to turn chaos into glory, and possibly not into a disaster!!!</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354000/extras/Slackers_B3_Discord.jpg?t=1734729744\" /><br><br><strong>Welcome in the wonderful and crazy world of Slackers!</strong><br><br><strong>Race solo or with your friends</strong> in one of the most reckless downhill rides ever! Discover and master the<strong> unpredictable and unique movements of a shopping cart</strong>, find your shortcuts, collecting drinks along the way to satisfy your thirst and push yourself to <strong>crazy speeds across 16 different tracks</strong> to reach the store before it closes!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354000/extras/Slackers_B4_Discord.jpg?t=1734729744\" /><br><br><strong>KEY CONCEPT</strong><br><br><strong>-</strong> You can live the dream of racing on a shopping cart at crazy speeds (risk free)<br><strong>-</strong> If you're afraid to do it alone, you can play with 3 friends online<br><strong>-</strong> Collect the drinks along the track to refill the stamina<br><strong>-</strong> The store is closing; you'd better hurry up!<br><br><strong>THINGS TO REMEMBER ONCE YOU'RE IN THE CART:</strong><br><br><strong>- First of all: I'ts not a car.</strong> <br><strong>- The cart has no brakes.</strong> (deal with it)<br><strong>- The cart has no engine.</strong> (push and sweat to move).<br><strong>- The cart has no seatbelts.</strong> (we all know how it's going to end)<br><strong>- The cart has no steering wheel</strong> (good luck in taming th